    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly with no known leaks or mechanical issues, and the transmission shifts precisely as it should. While the interior is clean and free of major stains or tears, there is some minor cosmetic wear on the driver's seat and a few small stone chips on the front bumper. All electronics and climate control systems are fully functional, making this a reliable and comfortable choice for its next owner.",
